Package com.example.finding_tory

Class Item

java.lang.Object
com.example.finding_tory.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Item extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an item with various attributes such as purchase date, description, make, model, serial number, estimated value, comments, and tags. This class is designed to be serializable to facilitate easy storage and retrieval.
